########################################################
  shellinford: succinct document retrieval library
  author     : echizen_tm
  last-update: Mar.9, 2012
########################################################

- how to install
$$ ./configure
$$ make
$$ make check
$$ sudo make install

- how to uninstall
$$ sudo make uninstall
$$ make clean

- use sample
$$ sample/make_fm_index var/test.txt.fm < var/test.txt
$$ sample/search_fm_index var/test.txt.fm
Holmes
2 hits.
[0]: Milky Holmes(1)
[2]: Sherlock Holmes(1)



